  1. Overview
    Adds 1100+ verified businesses distributed across all Italian regions.
    Businesses are categorized and distributed across major cities in each region.

  2. Regions Covered
    - Abruzzo (LAquila, Pescara, Teramo, Chieti)
    - Basilicata (Potenza, Matera)
    - Calabria (Catanzaro, Reggio Calabria, Cosenza)
    - Friuli-Venezia Giulia (Trieste, Udine, Pordenone, Gorizia)
    - Liguria (Genova, La Spezia, Savona, Imperia)
    - Marche (Ancona, Pesaro, Macerata, Ascoli Piceno)
    - Molise (Campobasso, Isernia)
    - Puglia (Bari, Lecce, Taranto, Foggia, Brindisi)
    - Sardegna (Cagliari, Sassari, Olbia, Nuoro)
    - Trentino-Alto Adige (Trento, Bolzano)
    - Umbria (Perugia, Terni)
    - Valle d'Aosta (Aosta)

  3. Categories Per City (30 types)
    - Restaurants, pizzerias, bars
    - Medical professionals (dentists, doctors, pharmacies, veterinarians)
    - Legal and financial professionals (lawyers, accountants, notaries)
    - Beauty services (hairdressers, beauty centers)
    - Craftsmen (plumbers, electricians, painters, blacksmiths, carpenters)
    - Retail (supermarkets, hardware stores, bakeries, butchers, fishmongers, bookstores)
    - Sports and wellness (gyms)
    - Professional services (architects, engineers, surveyors)
    - Automotive services (garages, tire shops)

  4. Security
    - All businesses are unclaimed (is_claimed = false) but verified
    - Each business has a unique VAT number
    - Each business has one primary location
*/

